@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Transition Diagram

initial : User is not logged in

state "User is not logged in" as A {}
state "Logged in - Teacher" as B {}
state "Logged in - Student" as C {}

A --> B : Log in with details
B --> B : Create new quiz
B --> B : Edit existing quiz
B --> B : Save quiz as draft
B --> B : Post quiz for students
B --> C : Continue as student

C --> C : Select quiz after notification
C --> D : Answer selected quiz
D --> E : Submit quiz
E --> F : View result

state "Logged in - Teacher" as B {}
state "Selected Quiz" as D {}
state "Answering Quiz" as E {}
state "View Result" as F {}

B --> A : Log out
C --> A : Log out

final : User is logged out
@enduml
